Package gov.nih.nlm.meme

Top-level package for all MEME applications.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Initializable Generically allows an application to give components known to require initialization an opportunity to do so before normal application processing proceeds.
InitializationContext Generically allows Initializable components to register themselves with the application that requested their initialzation.
MEMEConstants This interface holds constants commonly used by MEME applications.
 

Class Summary
MEMEMail Utility for sending email messages from MEME applications.
MEMEToolkit Utility class that has generic methods that the server/client can use.
MIDServices Utility for accessing NLM socket services.
Version The Version class provides package version information for gov.nih.nlm.meme package.
 

Package gov.nih.nlm.meme Description

Top-level package for all MEME applications.
